## Script Design
- Connects to MongoDB via existing `dbConnect()`
- Finds campaigns where `status` is missing or null: `{ $or: [{ status: { $exists: false } }, { status: null }] }`
- Updates matched documents with `$set: { status: 'active' }`
- Emits audit log with `startTime`, `endTime`, `matchedCount`, `modifiedCount`, `failures`
- Idempotent: re-running finds 0 matched documents if all are already backfilled
- Exits with code 1 on failure, code 0 on success

